---
import '../styles/global.css'
---
<html lang="en">
  <body class="bg-zinc-950 text-white">
    <header class="fixed top-0 right-0 p-4">
      <nav class="space-x-4">
        <a class="hover:underline" href="/">Home</a>
        <a class="hover:underline" href="/about">About</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 pb-16 pt-24">
      <h1 class="mb-6 text-4xl font-bold">About Me</h1>

      <p class="mb-4 leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
        Hi, I&apos;m Thalium (TLSenZ), a software engineering apprentice from Switzerland.
        I enjoy building things with code and spending time in the Linux ecosystem.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed text-zinc-200">
        This blog is where I share my learning journey, experiments, and projects.
        The site is still growing, but I&apos;m actively improving it and will publish more posts over time.
      </p>

      <section class="mb-8 rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">Quick Facts</h2>
        <ul class="list-inside list-disc space-y-2 text-zinc-200">
          <li><strong>Favorite Linux distro:</strong> Arch Linux</li>
          <li><strong>Favorite programming language:</strong> Rust</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-5">
        <h2 class="mb-3 text-xl font-semibold">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-200">
          Want to share feedback or just say hi?
          Reach me at
          <a class="text-blue-300 hover:underline" href="mailto:thalium@duck.com">thalium@duck.com</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
